Pre-Game Insights: Kobel confirmed on Wednesday: 'Playing in the national team is the greatest thing. It was already my dream as a little boy. So I was very pleased. I think that's normal,' says the 26-year-old with a broad grin.
Yakin: 'We want to play successful football and are taking the Nations League very seriously because it's also important for the World Cup qualifiers.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: Gregor Kobel has replaced Yann Sommer as number 1.
Yakin: 'I'm delighted, also for Gregor Kobel, for whom it's a new situation.'
